data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
Note: Neptune2/3 units with firmware earlier than v6.0.4A have a bug which causes any jumps made after August 31, 2017 to be logged as if they had been made 128 months prior. Since Alti-2 does not seem interested in fixing this bug on Neptune2, we can try to work around the issue ourselves.
Set the box above to the date of the earliest valid jump in your logbook. Any jumps whose date appears to be earlier than this date will have the date bug workaround applied to them.
